The paper discusses the use of Deep Reinforcement Learning to navigate through unsignaled intersections, which involves decision-making and control of autonomous vehicles. This falls under the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of active sensing behaviors, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY).
